|--------|-----------|---------------|-----------------|
| `create_profiles_table.sql` | Crear tabla profiles + RLS | `profiles` | ⚠️ Verificar |
| `create_messaging_tables.sql` | Crear threads + messages + RLS | `threads`, `messages` | ⚠️ Verificar |
