**RLS Policies**:
- SELECT: Participants only (`auth.uid() = user1_id OR auth.uid() = user2_id`)
- INSERT: Participants only (`auth.uid() = user1_id OR auth.uid() = user2_id`)
- UPDATE/DELETE: Denied (MVP: no editing/deleting threads)

