Función: hasProfile()

Código actual:
```typescript
export async function hasProfile() {
  const supabase = createServerSupabaseClient()

  const { data: { session } } = await supabase.auth.getSession()
  if (!session) {
    return false
  }

  const { data: profile } = await supabase
    .from('profiles')
    .select('user_id')
    .eq('user_id', session.user.id)
    .maybeSingle()

  return !!profile
}
```

